sc_cat_item_producer.description:
Student can fill this form to apply for leave.

  • Fill all the mandatory fields marked with (*).
  • Strict action will be taken against false documents.

 

Please ensure the following conditions are met while filling the form:

  • Leave Application must be submitted 10 days in advance.
  • It is mandatory to submit medical documents for medical leave.
  • Only emergency leaves can be taken immediately (No 10 days notice required).
sc_cat_item_producer.name: Apply For Leave
